<p>The problem is that all the Hexapod assembly guides I've read (including the one above which I'm using) say that the servos on the coxa link have to be installed in a way that the Zero angles (the angle the servos move to automatically when they're plugged in) of the servos should point to look like this from above: 
(the red circles are the servos in question)</p>

<p><a href="https://i.stack.imgur.com/aYNa2.png" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><img src="https://i.stack.imgur.com/aYNa2.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>

